@pixel-sheet v1

@sprite sprite:hero
description Universal 16x16 humanoid model. Knight, ranger, wizard, rogue, woodcutter, companions and skeletons are all palette swaps of this one grid.
grid 16x16
anchor 8,16
channels S,s,R,r,W,F,f,X
palette palette:base
facing mirror-x 1
animations idle=anim:idle,walk=anim:walk-bob,hurt=anim:hit-flash,ghost=anim:trail-fade
