@sprite sprite:princess
description 16x16 gowned figure. Princess Amber by default; Mage Gwydion is the wizard palette swap of this grid.
grid 16x16
anchor 8,16
channels G,R,F,f,P,p,X
palette palette:base
facing mirror-x 1
animations idle=anim:idle,walk=anim:walk-bob,hurt=anim:hit-flash
traits Transform,Sprite,Palette,Facing,Animator,DepthSorted
rows
................
......XGGX......
.....XGRRGX.....
....XGGGGGGX....
....XGFFFFGX....
...XGFFXFFXX....
...XGFfFFFfX....
....XGFFFFGX....
.....GXFFXG.....
.....XPPPPX.....
....XXpPPpXX....
....XPPPPPPX....
...XXpPPPPpXX...
...XPPPPPPPPX...
...XXXXXXXXXX...
................
@end

@sprite sprite:dragon
